SELECT    INITCAP(x5.display_name)                                AS guest_display_name,
          Lower(x5.email)                                         AS guest_email,
          INITCAP(x6.display_name)                                AS host_display_name,
          Lower(x6.email)                                         AS host_email,
                    CONCAT(x6.phone_country_code,x6.phone_number) AS host_phone,
          x1.ref_no                                               AS id,
          x1.status,
          x2.registration_no,
          x2.url,
          x4.NAME                                                           AS brand,
          x3.NAME                                                           AS model,
          to_char(x1.request_start_at + interval '8 hours','Day, dd Month') AS request_start_date,
          to_char(x1.request_start_at + interval '8 hours','hh12:miAM')     AS request_start_time,
          to_char(x1.request_end_at   + interval '8 hours','Day, dd Month') AS request_end_date,
          to_char(x1.request_end_at   + interval '8 hours','hh12:miAM')     AS request_end_time,
          CASE
                    WHEN x2.is_instant = true THEN x1.created_at+interval '8 hours'
                    ELSE x11.created_at                         +interval '8 hours'
          END AS accepted_at,
          d1.rental,
          d2.insurance,
          CASE WHEN d3.pickup IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE d3.pickup END AS pickup,
          CASE WHEN d4.dropoff IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE d4.dropoff END AS dropoff,
          CASE WHEN d3.pickup IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE d3.pickup end + CASE WHEN d4.dropoff IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE d4.dropoff end as delivery_fee,
          CASE WHEN x7.discount_amount IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE x7.discount_amount END AS discount,
          x1.gross_amount,
          x1.net_amount,
          CASE WHEN x8.pickup_address IS NULL THEN 'N/A' ELSE x8.pickup_address END AS pickup_address,
          CASE WHEN x9.dropoff_address IS NULL THEN 'N/A' ELSE x9.dropoff_address END AS dropoff_address,
          x10.listing_address
          , CASE WHEN mf.amount IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE mf.amount END AS mileage_purchased
          , TO_CHAR(x1.created_at, 'DD Mon YYYY, HH12:MIAM') AS created_time
          , CEIL(EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM (request_end_at - request_start_at)) / 86400)*200 as mileage
FROM      bookings x1
LEFT JOIN listings x2
ON        x1.listing_id=x2.id
LEFT JOIN models x3
ON        x2.model_id=x3.id
LEFT JOIN brands x4
ON        x3.brand_id=x4.id
LEFT JOIN users x5
ON        x1.user_id=x5.id
LEFT JOIN users x6
ON        x2.user_id=x6.id
LEFT JOIN booking_common_promos x7
ON        x1.id=x7.booking_id
LEFT JOIN booking_lines mf ON mf.booking_id = x1.id
    AND mf.slug = 'mileage-fee'
LEFT JOIN
          (
                    SELECT    t1.booking_id,
                                        concat(t2.address_line_1, ' ', t2.address_line_2, ' ', t2.state_region_province, ' ', t2.postal_code, ' ', t2.country) AS pickup_address
                    FROM      booking_deliveries t1
                    LEFT JOIN user_address t2
                    ON        t1.delivery_id = t2.id
                    WHERE     t1.type = 'car-pick-up') x8
ON        x1.id=x8.booking_id
LEFT JOIN
          (
                    SELECT    t1.booking_id,
                                        concat(t2.address_line_1, ' ', t2.address_line_2, ' ', t2.state_region_province, ' ', t2.postal_code, ' ', t2.country) AS dropoff_address
                    FROM      booking_deliveries t1
                    LEFT JOIN user_address t2
                    ON        t1.delivery_id = t2.id
                    WHERE     t1.type = 'car-drop-off') x9
ON        x1.id=x9.booking_id
LEFT JOIN
          (
                   SELECT   listing_id,
                                     concat(address_line_1, ' ', address_line_2, ' ', state_region_province, ' ',postal_code, ' ', country) AS listing_address,
                            CASE
                                     WHEN rank () OVER (partition BY listing_id ORDER BY created_at+interval '8 hours' DESC)=1 THEN 'Y'
                                     ELSE 'N'
                            END AS latest_update
                   FROM     listing_location ) x10
ON        x1.listing_id = x10.listing_id
AND       x10.latest_update='Y'
LEFT JOIN host_tracking x11
ON        x1.id=x11.booking_id
AND       x11.status='accepted'
LEFT JOIN
          (
                 SELECT booking_id,
                        amount AS rental
                 FROM   booking_lines
                 WHERE  slug = 'rental-fee') d1
ON        x1.id = d1.booking_id
LEFT JOIN
          (
                 SELECT booking_id,
                        amount AS insurance
                 FROM   booking_lines
                 WHERE  NAME IN ('SCDW',
                                 'Lite',
                                 'Standard',
                                 'Premium') ) d2
ON        x1.id = d2.booking_id
LEFT JOIN
          (
                 SELECT booking_id,
                        amount AS pickup
                 FROM   booking_lines
                 WHERE  slug = 'car-pick-up-fee') d3
ON        x1.id = d3.booking_id
LEFT JOIN
          (
                 SELECT booking_id,
                        amount AS dropoff
                 FROM   booking_lines
                 WHERE  slug = 'car-drop-off-fee') d4
ON        x1.id = d4.booking_id
WHERE     COALESCE(x11.created_at,x1.created_at)>=now()-interval '5 Minutes'
AND       x1.currency='myr'
AND       x1.status='accepted'
ORDER BY  x11.created_at DESC
